<p><strong>FT Weekend Magazine, The Office: A Photography Special</strong></p>
<p>After a year of remote working, FT Weekend’s first issue of 2021 took an in-depth look at the office through the lens of great imagemaking. The cover features a photograph taken from American artist and educator Endia Beal’s series Performance Review. Shot in her childhood home using a projector, the image offers a clever reimagining of what is, let’s face it, not always the sexiest of visual subjects.</p>
